query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.name,
  COALESCE(p.ci, 'null') as ci,
  COALESCE(p.fci, 'null') as fci,
  COALESCE(p.deferredMaintenanceCost, 'null') as deferredMaintenanceCost,
  COALESCE(p.currentReplacementValue, 'null') as currentReplacementValue,
  COALESCE(p.lastCalculatedAt, 'null') as lastCalculatedAt
FROM projects p
WHERE p.id IN (
  SELECT DISTINCT ast.projectId 
  FROM assessments a 
  JOIN assets ast ON a.assetId = ast.id
)
ORDER BY p.id
LIMIT 20;
